# Paste into Railway → the service that runs THIS API (the Docker/web service), NOT the Postgres service.
#
# Security: set NODE_ENV=production on this service. Secrets (below) must exist ONLY here — never on a
# static/frontend service or in VITE_* variables (those ship to the browser).
#
# CORS (browser → API): default production allowlist is https://app.interpreterai.org only.
# For extra origins (e.g. preview URL), set a comma-separated list:
# CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://app.interpreterai.org,https://your-preview.up.railway.app
# Variables tab → New Variable → choose "Variable Reference" and pick Postgres → DATABASE_URL,
# or paste the line below using your database service’s exact name from the project canvas.
#
# Common reference (default Postgres plugin name is "Postgres"):
DATABASE_URL=${{Postgres.DATABASE_URL}}
#
# If your DB service is named differently, match it exactly, e.g.:
# DATABASE_URL=${{PostgreSQL.DATABASE_URL}}
#
# Optional (private networking / some templates):
# DATABASE_PRIVATE_URL=${{Postgres.DATABASE_PRIVATE_URL}}

# ── Live transcription (Soniox) — same API service as DATABASE_URL above ──
SONIOX_API_KEY=
# Aliases: SONIOX_STT_API_KEY, SONIOX_KEY, SONIOX_API_TOKEN (case-insensitive names OK)

# ── Translation / terminology (OpenAI) ──
OPENAI_API_KEY=

# ── Transactional email (Resend) — server only, never exposed to the client ──
RESEND_API_KEY=
#
# Immediate / manual blasts (e.g. one-off trial reminder script in the API repo):
#   • No timezone variables are involved — only RESEND_API_KEY + DATABASE_URL on this service.
#   • Run from this service’s shell: cd artifacts/api-server && node --import tsx ./src/lib/send-trial-users-reminder-now.ts
#   • If sends fail, check Resend dashboard + logs for "Resend send failed", not TZ.
#
# Scheduled “trial active reminder” job (trial-active-reminder-job.ts):
#   • Primary: America/New_York calendar date + clock hour (product timezone).
#   • Set both or the job will not fire on that day:
# TRIAL_ACTIVE_REMINDER_SEND_ON_APP_DATE=2026-04-12
# TRIAL_ACTIVE_REMINDER_SEND_AFTER_APP_HOUR=10
#   • Legacy: TRIAL_ACTIVE_REMINDER_SEND_ON_UTC_DATE + TRIAL_ACTIVE_REMINDER_SEND_AFTER_UTC_HOUR
#     still work if SEND_ON_APP_DATE is unset (UTC semantics).
#
# Optional: TZ=UTC on this service for clearer logs (does not change when Resend delivers mail).
# TZ=UTC

# ── Google OAuth + sessions (if missing, /debug/ai-env lists them under missingInProcessEnv) ──
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=
# SESSION_SECRET=
# (or NEXTAUTH_SECRET)
